.SH NAME
commitbrief-completion-fish - Generate the autocompletion script for fish


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcommitbrief completion fish [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate the autocompletion script for the fish shell.

.PP
To load completions in your current shell session:

.EX
commitbrief completion fish | source
.EE

.PP
To load completions for every new session, execute once:

.EX
commitbrief completion fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/commitbrief.fish
.EE

.PP
You will need to start a new shell for this setup to take effect.


